{"tid":542342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粉嶺公路3賤種車撞兼懵撚壞車阻路　上水一帶交通塞閪爆","createTime":"2018-01-27T11:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T11:37:37.000Z","uid":23707,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e210714fb3256f0e60d43b32011429071f49a45d","tid":542342,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:18:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180127/bkn-20180127184939679-0127_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180127%2Fbkn-20180127184939679-0127_00822_001.html&d=I%2F3eFLj7bWMgLNl9OjOdfo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=1a1faeb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180127/bkn-20180127184939679-0127_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n上水又撚柒再發生大塞車！傍晚6時許，粉嶺公路往上水方向近嘉福邨，有3架由弱智人士同痙攣人士駕駛的私家車與1輛屎忽鬼仆街柒頭貨車相撞，導致7撚人受傷。在差不多時間雞嶺迴旋處又有垃圾廢柴車輛故障，行車線受阻，導致上水區一帶交通嚴柒重擠塞，屌你老味臭雞。 <br />\n<br />\n去年11月23日下午繁忙時間，因車多關係，上水一帶的路段一度出現交通擠塞，持續3小時始恢復正常，其實點柒止咁少。"},{"pid":"b21c6811b92bd381c9ae106b619a3fc9357457db","tid":542342,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/191934_527e57da72fc8c1f20062aad9728867f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F191934_527e57da72fc8c1f20062aad9728867f.png&h=88fcf8e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉事故障懵鳩車（百份報讀者提供）"},{"pid":"ecd1d9a02aba7fc1fe45e5efa66251387ad1df77","tid":542342,"uid":3668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:21:10.000Z","msg":"應該要公開肇事車主姓名以作懲戒"},{"pid":"8fc2964d7c0a1b9e1a8aef1451e0df962ea88220","tid":542342,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecd1d9a02aba7fc1fe45e5efa66251387ad1df77","tid":542342,"uid":3668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:21:10.000Z","msg":"應該要公開肇事車主姓名以作懲戒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:22:50.000Z","msg":"咁少？"},{"pid":"2c06ab155de7221fb2ec5af94dcf66d735944d3c","tid":542342,"uid":129474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:23:10.000Z","msg":"仆佢個街，我馬會道上閪嶺迴旋處想去嘉福，點知塞左3個字先到迴旋處，下個到我出車，慈母就封路唔比過，要我落高速大埔方向，佢老味"},{"pid":"4da0f70eb2266f73ff02da74c029303df971a6ef","tid":542342,"uid":13914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:24:01.000Z","msg":"真識揀地方壞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955336c00a9ec6fc87d90eda157d9ec70aa6a32f","tid":542342,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:25:36.000Z","msg":"每月一次活動"},{"pid":"67cad71f75600055e5781352fbcad15207774a2d","tid":542342,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4da0f70eb2266f73ff02da74c029303df971a6ef","tid":542342,"uid":13914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:24:01.000Z","msg":"真識揀地方壞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:29:48.000Z","msg":"食屎狗黎，垃圾車學人渣車街"},{"pid":"553cc7f661dcb549078ed78b92ee083c582a7570","tid":542342,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:33:46.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"8ed6aa85cb8b55b47ad59d45538e2634a10ccd2e","tid":542342,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:35:21.000Z","msg":"如果啲新聞係咁寫法實好睇好多"},{"pid":"bf61bc698ca0ca4f3c032575538eaa5be9edc860","tid":542342,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:37:37.000Z","msg":"死撚左佢啦屌 垃撚圾"}]}